{"id":["109587384977597149"],"username":["fatamorgana"],"acct":["fatamorgana@qoto.org"],"display_name":["Sarah Green"],"locked":[false],"bot":[false],"discoverable":[true],"group":[false],"created_at":["2022-12-27"],"note":["<p><a href=\"https://qoto.org/tags/Introduction\" class=\"mention hashtag\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">#<span>Introduction<\/span><\/a><\/p><p>I live on the shores of <a href=\"https://qoto.org/tags/LakeSuperior\" class=\"mention hashtag\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">#<span>LakeSuperior<\/span><\/a> on the <a href=\"https://qoto.org/tags/Keweenaw\" class=\"mention hashtag\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">#<span>Keweenaw<\/span><\/a> Peninsula in the <a href=\"https://qoto.org/tags/UpperPeninsula\" class=\"mention hashtag\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">#<span>UpperPeninsula<\/span><\/a> of <a href=\"https://qoto.org/tags/Michigan\" class=\"mention hashtag\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">#<span>Michigan<\/span><\/a>. This region is within Ojibwe Gichigami (“Ojibwa’s Great Sea”) homelands and ceded-territory, established by the TREATY OF 1842<\/p><p>I'm a professor of <a href=\"https://qoto.org/tags/environmental\" class=\"mention hashtag\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">#<span>environmental<\/span><\/a> <a href=\"https://qoto.org/tags/chemistry\" class=\"mention hashtag\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">#<span>chemistry<\/span><\/a> with an interest in everything related to <a href=\"https://qoto.org/tags/climate\" class=\"mention hashtag\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">#<span>climate<\/span><\/a>, including molecular to global aspects of the carbon cycle, energy and social transitions, new and old technologies for sustainability,  forests and biodiversity, local to international climate policy, and the systems thinking approaches we need to make progress.<\/p><p>Too much of a news and politics junkie than is healthy.<\/p><p>I share my homestead with a partner, a dog, several felines, two donkeys, plants, and occasional uninvited critters.<\/p><p><a href=\"https://qoto.org/tags/science\" class=\"mention hashtag\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">#<span>science<\/span><\/a> <a href=\"https://qoto.org/tags/LakeSuperior\" class=\"mention hashtag\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">#<span>LakeSuperior<\/span><\/a> <a href=\"https://qoto.org/tags/Keweenaw\" class=\"mention hashtag\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">#<span>Keweenaw<\/span><\/a> <a href=\"https://qoto.org/tags/Michigan\" class=\"mention hashtag\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">#<span>Michigan<\/span><\/a> <a href=\"https://qoto.org/tags/GreatLakes\" class=\"mention hashtag\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">#<span>GreatLakes<\/span><\/a> <a href=\"https://qoto.org/tags/Climate\" class=\"mention hashtag\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">#<span>Climate<\/span><\/a> <a href=\"https://qoto.org/tags/books\" class=\"mention hashtag\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">#<span>books<\/span><\/a> <a href=\"https://qoto.org/tags/yurt\" class=\"mention hashtag\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">#<span>yurt<\/span><\/a> <a href=\"https://qoto.org/tags/garden\" class=\"mention hashtag\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">#<span>garden<\/span><\/a> <a href=\"https://qoto.org/tags/cat\" class=\"mention hashtag\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">#<span>cat<\/span><\/a> <a href=\"https://qoto.org/tags/dog\" class=\"mention hashtag\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">#<span>dog<\/span><\/a> <a href=\"https://qoto.org/tags/donkey\" class=\"mention hashtag\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">#<span>donkey<\/span><\